W06_WRLD_SIUG_INITIAL_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W06_WRLD_SIUG_INITIAL_000_DETAIL.text: The Junction connected you to a twisty, squirmy world. Will you find anyone captivating here?

W06_EVAR_SIUG_RETURN_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W06_EVAR_SIUG_RETURN_000_DETAIL.text: You witnessed captivating darkness in this world, but the time has come to leave.

W06_EVAR_SIUG_KENZOKU_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W06_EVAR_SIUG_KENZOKU_000_DETAIL.text: Is this the place you are meant to receive your gift from the Kosmos?
